sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Operator as KubeRay Operator<br/>SA Token Auth
    participant HeadPod as Ray Head Pod<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    participant WorkerPods as Ray Worker Pods
    participant Submitter as Submitter Job Pod
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant RBACProxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant TokenReview as TokenReview API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant SAR as SubjectAccessReview API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User, Submitter: Flow 1: RayJob Execution via K8sJobMode

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply RayJob<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Watch event: RayJob created
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: RayCluster created
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Pods, Services<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    Note over HeadPod, WorkerPods: Ray cluster starts up
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create K8s Job (submitter)<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    Submitter->>HeadPod: POST /api/jobs<br/>HTTP/8265 (or mTLS)
    HeadPod-->>Submitter: Job ID
    loop Poll job status
        Operator->>HeadPod: GET /api/jobs/{id}<br/>HTTP/8265 (or mTLS)
        HeadPod-->>Operator: Job status
    end

    Note over User, SAR: Flow 2: Authenticated Dashboard Access via Gateway API (RHOAI)

    User->>Gateway: Browse Ray Dashboard<br/>HTTPS/443, OIDC Token
    Gateway->>RBACProxy: HTTPRoute match /ray/{ns}/{cluster}/<br/>HTTPS/8443, OIDC Token forwarded
    RBACProxy->>TokenReview: Validate OIDC token<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    TokenReview-->>RBACProxy: Token valid, user identity
    RBACProxy->>SAR: Check verb=get resource=services<br/>resourceName={cluster}-head-svc<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    SAR-->>RBACProxy: Allowed
    RBACProxy->>HeadPod: Proxy to localhost<br/>HTTP/8265 (local)
    HeadPod-->>RBACProxy: Dashboard HTML
    RBACProxy-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>User: Dashboard rendered

    Note over User, K8sAPI: Flow 3: RayService Zero-Downtime Upgrade

    User->>K8sAPI: Update RayService spec<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Watch event: RayService updated
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create pending RayCluster<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    Note over HeadPod: Pending cluster starts
    Operator->>HeadPod: POST /api/serve/config<br/>HTTP/8265, deploy new Serve config
    HeadPod-->>Operator: Config applied
    loop Check Serve health
        Operator->>HeadPod: GET /api/serve/deployments<br/>HTTP/8265
        HeadPod-->>Operator: Deployment status
    end
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Update serve-svc selector<br/>to pending cluster
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Delete old active RayCluster
